updates_from_previous_fiscal_note: This fiscal note is based on H.B. 1169, H.D. 1, S.D. 1, which has been amended to make the measure effective upon its approval. This amendment confirms the bill's immediate implementation, solidifying the fiscal analysis presented in the prior note which was based on the bill becoming a substantive measure after a previously inoperative effective date was removed. No other substantive changes affecting the fiscal impact of the measure have been identified.
